snippet.title: Gears 5 Launch Trailer - Gears Forever
snippet.description:
We're about to drop the biggest Gears EVER. Get ready for #Gears5.

Start playing Sept. 5th at 9pm local time with Xbox Game Pass Ultimate and Gears 5: Ultimate Edition Early Access.
